         VERSION=1.3
          
         UPDATED=20050408
           SPELL=PEAR-DB_ado
        WEB_SITE=http://pear.php.net/package/DB_ado/
      LICENSE[0]=LGPL
           SHORT='PEAR: DB driver which use MS ADODB library'
cat << EOF
DB_ado is a database independent query interface
definition for Microsoft's ADODB library using
PHP's COM extension.
This class allows you to connect to different
data sources like MS Access, MS SQL Server,
Oracle and other RDBMS on a Win32 operating
system.
Moreover the possibility exists to use MS Excel
spreadsheets, XML, text files and other not
relational data as data source.
EOF


